parameters.name: authType
parameters.description: The type of IAM policy. NONE: The resource does not use an IAM policy. This is the default. AWS_IAM: The resource uses an IAM policy. When this type is used, auth is enabled and an auth policy is required.

parameters.name: serviceIdentifier
parameters.description: The ID or ARN of the service.

nested_items.name: arn
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the service.

nested_items.name: certificateArn
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the certificate.

nested_items.name: customDomainName
nested_items.description: The custom domain name of the service.
